<section id="itsm_locQualityIssues">
    <title>locQualityIssues</title>
    <para>Localization Quality Issues - a standoff wrapper element to group any number of single issue elements related to the same span of source or target content.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Contains:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
        <member>- One or more <olink targetdoc="itsm_locQualityIssue.xml" targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssue"><code>&lt;locQualityIssue></code></olink>
            elements</member>
        
    </simplelist>
  
  <para><emphasis>Parents:</emphasis></para>
  
  <simplelist>
    <member>- <olink targetdoc="../structural/unit.xml"
      targetptr="unit"><code>&lt;unit></code></olink></member>
    
  </simplelist>
  

    <para><emphasis>Attributes:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
      <member>- <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_id.xml" targetptr="itsm_id">
        <code>xml:id</code>
      </olink>, <glossterm>required</glossterm>
    </member>
      <!--  not allowed on ITS stand off elements <member>-<olink targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_annotatorsRef.xml"
        targetptr="itsm_annotatorsRef">
        <code>annotatorsRef</code></olink>,
        <glossterm>optional</glossterm></member>-->
        
    </simplelist>

  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Constraints</title>
    <listitem>
      <para>Each <link linkend="itsm_locQualityIssues">locQualityIssues</link> element
        <glossterm>should</glossterm> be referenced by at least one <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_locQualityIssuesRef.xml"
          targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssuesRef"><code>locQualityIssuesRef</code></olink> attribute
        within the same <olink targetdoc="../strcutural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"><code>&lt;unit></code></olink> element as per Constraints
        for the <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_locQualityIssuesRef.xml"
          targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssuesRef"><code>locQualityIssuesRef</code></olink>
        attribute.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  

  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Processing Requirements</title>
    <listitem>
      <para><firstterm>Modifiers</firstterm> detecting an orphaned <link
        linkend="itsm_locQualityIssues">locQualityIssues</link> element
        <glossterm>may</glossterm> delete that <link linkend="itsm_locQualityIssues"
          >locQualityIssues</link> element.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
    
    
</section>
